title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jan 19 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jan 19 2022
description:
Biden presidency in free fall, Dems panic to keep power. Was Biden's MLK/George Floyd comparison that crazy? Buck's bout with wimpy covid has been no big deal. He jokes that it's like covid light: "less flavor, less calories." Boris Johnson lifts UK mask mandate, Biden doubles down on sending out millions of useless masks and tests. Clay asks, do we have to have hundreds of tests each, for every time we want to hang out with friends? Do we have to worry about RINOs backing Dems on filibuster?
